data.description: This rare home on acreage is ready for you with perimeter fencing, cross fencing, gated entrance and much more! The three bedroom, two bathroom home is well maintained, new roof (Oct 2023- photos coming) and features stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. You will love the oversized covered patio behind the home, and the two car carport in addition to the garage. Located on a quiet road, and only minutes from Weatherford, Eagle Mountain Lake, and Fort Worth.
